\caption{\label{fig:pn}reflectivity of two Ge films grown on Si wafers. One film was hole-doped (p-Ge) and one electron-doped (n-Ge). The thickness is 1 $\mu$m and the free carrier density is $2\cdot10^{19}$cm$^{-3}$ for electrons and $7\cdot10^{19}$cm$^{-3}$ for holes.}
